_json.gridTitle: The Budgeting Method That Changed My Life
_json.description: A step-by-step guide on the budgeting process that changed my financial life. This unique budgeting method combines the calendar method, the cash envelope method, and the paycheck method. I love how the system is easy to use, easy to follow, and allows you to save money and pay off debt, while still paying regular bills. It also is the only system that allows you to incorporate the cash envelope into your budget worksheet! #cashenvelopemethod #daveramsey #budget #savemoney #debt
